## Limitations

The analysis is based on publicly available information and expert opinions, which may not capture the full complexity of theological debates within the Catholic Church. Additionally, the interpretation of doctrinal development can vary among theologians and scholars, leading to differing conclusions about the extent of the Pope's authority to change doctrine. Further research into official Church documents and statements from the Vatican would provide a more comprehensive understanding of this issue.